<br>
Verant made a level limit on vox and nag to keep higher levels from farming em. While I'm normally an FCFS advocate, I'm willing to accept that didn't mean they just wanted you to level up an appropriate alt so you could keep farming it. They wanted to cut out a niche for the lower level dragon raider. <br>
<br>
If you want a vox/nag rotation that actually serves people wanting to do this with thier main character, you have to cut out the alts. If you are a member of a guild that CAN kill the other dragons, you shouldnt be wasting the time of the people who can't. <br>
